Opt link4 { v !v  v  v !v }
Opt link4 { v !v  v !v  v }
Opt link4 { v !v !v  v  v }

# ends have exactly one connector
Opt end2 { v  v !v }
Opt end2 { v !v  v }

Opt end3 { v  v !v !v }
Opt end3 { v !v  v !v }
Opt end3 { v !v !v  v }

Opt end4 { v  v !v !v !v }
Opt end4 { v !v  v !v !v }
Opt end4 { v !v !v  v !v }
Opt end4 { v !v !v !v  v }

